msgid "<phrase>reports view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pregled Izvještaja</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Income and Expenses"
msgstr "Prihodi i troškovi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:47
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The reports in this section show your income and expenses either for the "
#| "current month or for each month in the current year. Of course, the "
#| "duration of the overall report and the duration captured by each column "
#| "can be configured to your liking. Graphs and Pie Charts also may be "
#| "produced."
msgid ""
"The reports in this section show your income and expenses either for the "
"current month, for each month in the current year, or for each year. Of "
"course, the duration of the overall report and the duration captured by each "
"column can be configured to your liking. Various Graphs and Pie Charts also "
"may be produced."
msgstr ""
"Izvještaji u ovom odjelu prikazuju prihode i troškove za tekući mjesec ili "
"za svaki mjesec tekuće godine. Naravno, dužina cjelokupnog izvještaja i "
"dužina svake kolone može biti podešena kako vam odgovara. Grafovi i kružni "
"grafovi također mogu biti prikazani."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Net Worth"
msgstr "Neto vrijednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here there are reports that describe your net worth, either at the current "
"moment, every month for the current year, or every year of your history. In "
"addition, there is a 7-day Cash Flow Forecast and a Net Worth Graph. There "
"are also reports to get the balances for all of your accounts at any given "
"point in time."
msgstr ""
"Tu se nalaze izvještaji koji opisuju vašu neto vrijednost, za tekući mjesec, "
"za svaki mjesec tekuće godine, ili za svaku godinu u vašoj historiji. "
"Dodatno, tu su i sedmodnevna prognoza protoka gotovine i grafik neto "
"vrijednosti. Također, tu su i izvještaji stanja svih vaših računa u bilo "
"kojem trenutku."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions"
msgstr "Transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section includes reports that list individual transactions. This is the "
"best way to print your account register for a specific period of time. The "
"transactions printed can be grouped together according to your liking by "
"choosing the appropriate report, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dio uključuje izvještaje koji izlistavaju pojedinačne transakcije. Ovo "
"je najbolji način za printanje registra vašeg računa za određeni vremenski "
"period. Transakcije koje se printaju mogu biti grupisane po vašoj želji "
"biranjem odgovarajućeg izvještaja, kao što su:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Account"
msgstr "Po računu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Category"
msgstr "Po kategoriji"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Month or Week"
msgstr "Po mjesecu ili sedmici"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Payee"
msgstr "Po primatelju uplate"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Reconciliation Status"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Tag"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cash Flow"
msgstr "Protok gotovine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Cash Flow report is similar to a Transaction report, but it displays "
#| "all cash-flow related transactions."
msgid ""
"The Cash Flow report is similar to a Transaction report, but it displays all "
"cash-flow related transactions for the specified period, which defaults to "
"the current month."
msgstr ""
"Izvještaj protoka gotovine je sličan transakcijskom izvještaju, ali "
"prikazuje sve transakcije vezane za protok gotovine."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investments"
msgstr "Ulaganja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These reports help you keep track of your investments. They only include "
"investment accounts. There are a variety of presentation filters and styles, "
"as shown in this partial list."
msgstr ""
"Ovi izještaji vam pomažu da pratite vaša ulaganja. Oni uključuju "
"investicione račune. Postoje razni načini i stilovi prezentovanja, koji su "
"prikazani u ovoj parcijalnoj listi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:98
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Investment Transactions: Similar to a Transactions report, and includes "
#| "the share price and quantities."
msgid ""
"Investment Transactions: Similar to a Transactions report, but it includes "
"share prices and quantities."
msgstr ""
"Investicione transakcije: slične transakcijskom izvještaju, uključuju cijenu "
"dionica i količine."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Investment Holdings by Account: Shows the current shares, price, and "
#| "value for each account."
msgid ""
"Investment Holdings by Account: Shows the current shares, prices, and values "
"for each account."
msgstr ""
"Posjed investicija po računu: pokazuje trenutne dionici, cijenu, i "
"vrijednost za svaki račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Investment Holdings by Type: Same as the previous report, but organizes "
#| "the accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, etc)"
msgid ""
"Investment Holdings by Type: Same as the previous report, but organizes the "
"accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Posjed investicija po tipu: isto kao i prethodni izvještaj, ali organizira "
"račune po tipu (dionice, zajednički fond, itd)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Performance by Account: Shows the annualized performance over any "
"period of time. This performs a cash flow analysis of all money coming into "
"and going out of the account. As a result, this is a very accurate picture "
"of how well your investments are doing."
msgstr ""
"Performanse investicija po računu: pokazuje performanse tokom bilo kojeg "
"perioda. Izvršava analizu protoka gotovine koja dolazi i odlazi sa računa. "
"Kao rezultat, ovo je vrlo dostojan prikaz toga koliko dobro vam investicije "
"funkcionišu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:116
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Investment Performance by Type: Same as the previous report, but "
#| "organizes the accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, etc)"
msgid ""
"Investment Performance by Type: Same as the previous report, but organizes "
"the accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Performanse investicija po tipu: Isto kao prethodni izvještaj, ali "
"organizira račune po tipu (dionice, zajednički fond, itd)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are also graphs for Investment Prices and Investment Worth."
msgstr ""
"Također, tu su grafovi za cijene investicija i vrijednosti investicija."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Porezi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The tax reports are just like the transactions reports, with the addition "
#| "that only Tax related categories are included. This allows you to flag "
#| "certain categories as being tax-related, and then get one big report at "
#| "the end of the year to see them all in one place. They may be listed "
#| "either by Category or by Payee, and for the last fiscal year."
msgid ""
"The tax reports are just like the transactions reports, with the addition "
"that only Tax related categories are included. This allows you to flag "
"certain categories as being tax-related, and then get one big report at the "
"end of the year to see the transactions for those categories all in one "
"place. They may be listed either by Category or by Payee, and for the last "
"fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"Porezni izvještaji su isti kao i transakcijski izvještaji, sa dodatkom da su "
"uključene samo kategorije vezane za porez. Ovo vam omogućava da označite "
"pojedine kategorije kao vezane za porez, i onda dobijete jedan veliki "
"izvještaj na kraju godine na kojem se vide sve na jednom mjestu. Mogu biti "
"izlistane po kategoriji ili po primaocu uplate, i za posljednju fiskalnu "
"godinu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budgeting"
msgstr "Određivanje budžeta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The budgeting reports are similar to net worth reports, but the reports can "
"display the budget for a given year, or even compare it to the actual income "
"and expenses for the same period."
msgstr ""
"Budžetni izvještaji su slični izvještajima o neto vrijednosti, ali mogu "
"prikazati budžet za bilo koju godinu, ili čak uporediti ga sa stvarnim "
"prihodima i troškovima za isti period."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forecast"
msgstr "Prognoza"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The forecast reports are just like the net worth reports, but they use the "
"information to display forecast information. You can display the information "
"at various levels and for the time frame of your choosing."
msgstr ""
"Izvještaji o prognozi su isti kao izvještaji o neto vrijednosti, ali oni "
"koriste informacije da prikažu informacije o prognozi. Možete prikazati "
"informacije na raznim nivoima i za vremenski okvir po vašem izboru."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informacija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:153
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "These reports display non-transaction information about schedules, "
#| "accounts, and loans."
msgid ""
"These reports display non-transaction information about accounts, loans, and "
"schedules."
msgstr ""
"Ovi izvještaji prikazuju informacije koje nisu vezane za transakcije o "
"rasporedima, računima i kreditima."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Charts"
msgstr "Dijagrami"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:160
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts\">Charts</link> are enabled, "
#| "this section lists all the reports which are marked to display a "
#| "graphical chart as the default. They are also listed in one of the other "
#| "sections, but they are also aggregated here for your easy reference."
msgid ""
"If <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts\">Charts</link> are enabled, this "
"section lists all the reports which are marked to display a graphical chart "
"as the default. They are also listed in one of the other sections, but they "
"are aggregated here for your easy reference."
msgstr ""
"Ako su <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts\">Dijagrami</link> uključeni, "
"ovaj dio izlistava sve izvještaje koji su unaprijed označeni  za prikaz "
"grafičkih dijagrama. Također su izlistani u jednom od ostalih dijelova, ali "
"su takođe zadržani ovdje da biste se lakše orijentisali."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorite Reports"
msgstr "Omiljeni izvještaji"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This section lists all the reports you have marked as a favorite in the "
#| "report configuration dialog. They are still listed in one of the other "
#| "sections, but they are also aggregated here for your easy reference. "
#| "Favorite reports are also included on the financial summary page for even "
#| "easier reference."
msgid ""
"This section lists all the reports you have marked as a favorite in the "
"report configuration dialog. They are still listed in one of the other "
"sections, but they are aggregated here for your easy reference. Favorite "
"reports can also be included on the Home View for even easier reference."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dio izlistava sve izvještaje koje ste označili kao omiljene u dijalogu "
"za konfiguraciju izvještaja. Izlistani su u jednom od ostalih dijelova, ali "
"su zadržani ovdje da biste se lakše orijentisali. Omiljeni izvještaji su "
"također uključeni na stranici finansijskog zaključka za još lakšu "
"orijentaciju."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working With Reports"
msgstr "Rad sa izvještajima"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are a number of actions you can take on each report. You can access "
#| "these by right-clicking the report name in the list of reports. "
#| "Alternately, once you have run a report, there are buttons across the top "
#| "of the view to invoke each of these:"
msgid ""
"There are a number of actions you can take on each report. You can access "
"some these by right-clicking the report name in the list of reports, which "
"brings up the <guilabel>Report options</guilabel> context menu. Alternately, "
"once you have run a report, there are buttons across the top of the view to "
"invoke each of these:"
msgstr ""
"Postoje razne akcije koje možete poduzeti za svaki izvještaj. Možete im "
"pristupiti desnim klikom na ime izvještaja u listi izvještaja. Drugi način "
"je da kada ste već pokrenuli zahtjev za izvještaj, možete vidjeti tipke koje "
"se nalaze na vrhu ekrana koje pozivaju sljedeće akcije:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Chart: Only present if the report is capable of displaying a chart. Clicking "
"this option toggles between the report and the chart."
msgstr ""
"Dijagram: Prisutan samo ako je izvještaj sposoban za prikaz dijagrama. "
"Klikom na ovu opciju prelazite sa izvještaja na dijagram i obrnuto."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:193
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Configure: Change the properties of this report. You can customize the "
#| "report to your liking and save it for future use."
msgid ""
"Configure report: Change the properties of this report. You can customize "
"the report to your liking and save it for future use. See the next section "
"for more details"
msgstr ""
"Konfiguriši: Promijeni osobine ovog izvještaja. Možete podesiti izvještaj "
"kako vam odgovara i sačuvati ga za kasniju upotrebu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "New: Create a new customized report based on the selected report."
msgid ""
"New report: Create a new, customized report based on the selected report."
msgstr "Novi: Kreiraj novi podešeni izvještaj na osnovu odabranog izvještaja."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export report: Reports can be exported, or saved, in &HTML; or CSV format. "
"&HTML; is intended to preserve the displayed formatting of the report. CSV "
"exports the data underlying the report."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:207
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Delete: Customized reports can be deleted. The default reports that ship "
#| "with &kappname; cannot be deleted."
msgid ""
"Delete report: Customized reports can be deleted. The default reports that "
"ship with &kmymoney; cannot be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Obriši: Podešeni izvještaji mogu biti obrisani. Unaprijed definisani "
"izvještaji koji su dostavljeni putem &kappname; ne mogu biti izbrisani."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Close report</guilabel> button was removed in 5.2. To close "
"the current report tab, click the small <guilabel>x</guilabel> to the right "
"of the report name on the tab."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Reports"
msgstr "Konfiguracija izvještaja"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with custom reports"
msgstr "Rad se podešenim izvještajima"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:223
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can configure the default reports or create your own from them by "
#| "selecting 'New' and then configuring the new report. When you select "
#| "'Configure' you will be presented with the Report Tab. Initially, it is "
#| "named the same as the old report with <quote>(Customized)</quote> added "
#| "to the end. You can change the name to whatever you want. You can even "
#| "name your custom reports the same as a default report, or the same as "
#| "another custom report. Also, you can always use the Comment field to "
#| "further distinguish reports."
msgid ""
"You can configure the default reports or create your own from them by "
"selecting <guilabel>New report</guilabel>, and then configuring the new "
"report. When you click <guilabel>Configure report</guilabel> you will be "
"presented with the Report Tab of the <guilabel>Report Configuration</"
"guilabel> dialog. Initially, the new report it is named the same as the old "
"report with <quote>(Customized)</quote> added to the end. You can change the "
"name to whatever you want. You can even name your custom reports the same as "
"a default report, or the same as another custom report. You can use the "
"Comment field to further distinguish reports."
msgstr ""
"Možete konfigurisati unaprijed definisane izvještaje ili kreirati vaš "
"vlastiti pomoću njih biranjem  'Novi' i onda konfigurisanjem novog "
"izvještaja. Kada odaberete 'Konfiguriši' biće vam prikazan kartica za "
"izvještaj. Na početku, ime mu je isto kao i starom izvještaju sa "
"<quote>(Customized)</quote> dodanim na kraju. Možete promijeniti ime kako "
"god želite. Čak možete  svojim podešenim izvještajima dati ime koje ima "
"unaprijed definisani izvještaj, ili mu dati ime koje ima neki drugi podešeni "
"izvještaj. Također, uvijek možete koristit polje za komentar za pravljenje "
"razlike među izvještajima."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Report Configuration dialog has a <guilabel>Report</guilabel> tab and a "
"<guilabel>Filters</guilabel> tab, which each have a number of subtabs. Each "
"subtab displays options for configuring different aspects of the report. "
"Note that specific subtabs and options within them may not appear if they "
"are not relevant to the report being configured."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report Tab"
msgstr "Kartica izvještaja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you configure general information about the report as well as "
"controlling details about what data is presented and how it is presented."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "General subtab"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:251
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Reports View</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>report configuration report tab general subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pregled Izvještaja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report configuration report tab general subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:262
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "On this tab, you set the basic properties of this report."
msgid "Here you set the basic properties of the report."
msgstr "U ovoj kartici, postavljate osnovna svojstva ovog izvještaja."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:266
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Report Name: Choose a name for this report."
msgid "Report Name: Choose or edit the name for this report."
msgstr "Ime izvještaja: Odaberite ime za ovaj izvještaj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:269
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Comment: Enter a comment to help you remember the details of this report."
msgid ""
"Comment: Enter a comment to help you remember the details of this report and "
"identify it if the name is the same as any other report."
