#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ring Chart"
msgstr "Prstenasti grafikon"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ring chart is very similar to a pie chart, except there is one "
"<quote>ring</quote> for each time slice in the report."
msgstr ""
"Prstenasti grafikon je veoma sličan tortnom grafikonu, osim što se koristi "
"po jedan <quote>prsten</quote> za svaki vremenski komad u izvještaju."

